ckground-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: inherit; line-height: 18px; background: transparent;\">TL 0.81 *0:1/4* 0.89</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: inherit; line-height: 18px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: inherit; line-height: 18px; background: transparent;\">TX 0.80 *2 3/4* 0.90</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: inherit; line-height: 18px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh m\u1ea5t \u0111i 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 tay FLC Thanh H\u00f3a l\u00e0 V\u0169 Minh Tu\u1ea5n v\u00e0 Minh T\u00f9ng. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u1ea9m Ph\u1ea3 v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o top 3 chung cu\u1ed9c. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n t\u00e0i ba Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng...</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: inherit; line-height: 18px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">C\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t nh\u01b0 Trung Hi\u1ebfu, H\u1ea3i Huy hay H\u1ed3ng Qu\u00e2n, Nghi\u00eam Xu\u00e2n T\u00fa...v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u1ed5i tr\u1ed9i \u1edf V.League. Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n c\u1ea3, s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 m\u00e0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu. Ngo\u00e0i ra, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ngo\u1ea1i binh Edyson - Vinicius c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: inherit; line-height: 18px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n, \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed l\u00e1i tr\u01b0\u1edfng khi Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng thay th\u1ebf Hu\u1ef3nh \u0110\u1ee9c. V\u1ec1 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, th\u00ec HLV tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng. V\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Huy To\u00e0n - Ng\u1ecdc Th\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u00fap SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n h\u01a1n \u1edf 2 b\u00ean c\u00e1nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"AbdVideoInPagePlayerWrapper\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: inherit; line-height: 18px; background: transparent; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: inherit; line-height: 18px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">\u0110\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo \u0111ang d\u1ea7n xu\u1ed1ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00ec n\u0103m nay, s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 33. Tuy r\u1eb1ng \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t, hay SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng c\u00f3 l\u1ea5y v\u1ec1 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Diogo m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u01a1i cho B.B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, th\u00ec b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1ee9 danh c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: inherit; line-height: 18px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra qu\u00e2n V.League 2018, Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean, ngo\u00e0i l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n, th\u00ec s\u00e2n C\u1ea9m Ph\u1ea3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh 'c\u1ed9ng d\u1ed3n' c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ecf. B\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 h\u1ecd b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 7 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u1eeba qua tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 5 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, so tr\u00ean sa b\u00e0n th\u00ec HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: inherit; line-height: 18px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: inherit; line-height: 18px; background: transparent;\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: inherit; line-height: 18px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh: Tu\u1ea5n Linh, Huy C\u01b0\u1eddng, Thanh H\u00e0o, V\u0103n Khoa, Xu\u00e2n H\u00f9ng, Qu\u00e1ch T\u00e2n, H\u1ea3i Huy, Xu\u00e2n T\u00fa, H\u1ed3ng Qu\u00e2n, Edyson,&nbsp;Vinicius.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: inherit; line-height: 18px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng: Thanh B\u00ecnh, Anh Quang, V\u0103n Long, Thanh Th\u1ecbnh, \u0110\u1ee9c L\u1ec5, Ti\u1ebfn D\u1ee5ng, Minh T\u00e2m, Ng\u1ecdc Th\u1eafng, Huy To\u00e0n, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: inherit; line-height: 18px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: inherit; line-height: 18px; background: transparent;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n</strong>&nbsp;2-0.</p>\r\n</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-4-3-barca-danh-ao-so-7-cho-griezmann-c409a942583.html","id":"415"},{"date":"Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt, ng\u00e0y 11/03/2018 05:05 AM (GMT+7)","title":"HLV Mourinho h\u1ea3 h\u00ea, Jurgen Klopp cay c\u00fa v\u00ec thua Man Utd","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"https://media.thethao247.vn/upload/kienlv/2018/03/11/231241.jpg","new_desc":"<p style=\"\"><strong>Man Utd \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool</strong> \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ecf xa ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1edbi 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 hai tr\u00ean BXH. Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn derby n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Rashford (2 b\u00e0n) v\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Bailly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y MU ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng \u00edt h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ch\u01a1i \u1edf th\u1ebf ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. HLV Mourinho ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ec1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea hay b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec. \u00d4ng ch\u1ec9 vui v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh MU \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</p><p style=\"\">T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y th\u00e0nh 2 ph\u1ea7n. Hi\u1ec7p 1 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Man Utd v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7p 2 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Liverpool. Theo quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a Man Utd l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nguy hi\u1ec3m.</p><p style=\"\">\u1ede hi\u1ec7p 2, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 quan \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c. Nh\u01b0ng theo t\u00f4i, Liverpool ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0ng Man Utd l\u1ea1i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t, ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hay nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng nguy hi\u1ec3m m\u00e0 Liverpool t\u1ea1o ra. V\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y\".</p><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://media.thethao247.vn/upload/namnv/2018/03/10/hahe.jpg\" alt=\"mu 2-1 liverpool, ngoai hang anh, hlv mourinho, hlv klopp\" title=\"Trong khi HLV Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh MU x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1eafng th\u00ec Klopp \u0111\u00f2i penalty\"><p style=\"\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Man Utd. \"\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 qu\u1ea3 penalty r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng khi Fellaini ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Sadio Mane. \u1ede nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn\", HLV Klopp kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i.</p><p style=\"\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Jurgen Klopp t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 khi \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1ng ra ph\u1ea3i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u1edf nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thua \u1edf 1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u hay tranh ch\u1ea5p v\u1edbi Romelu Lukaku nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng ph\u00eda sau v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p. Hai b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Man Utd trong th\u1ebf b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i\".</p>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-4-3-barca-danh-ao-so-7-cho-griezmann-c409a942583.html","id":"412"},{"date":"Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt, ng\u00e0y 11/03/2018 05:05 AM (GMT+7)","title":"HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ch\u1ec9 ra 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a HAGL","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"https://media.thethao247.vn/upload/kienlv/2018/03/11/231241.jpg","new_desc":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u qua 10/3, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i V.League 2018 g\u1eb7p B.B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 d\u1ed3n \u00e9p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong su\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chia \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n b\u1ecb ch\u00ea ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec. Tuy nhi\u00ean HLV HAGL \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh l\u1ea1i cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, trong \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 Tu\u1ea5n Anh.</p>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://media.thethao247.vn/upload/kienlv/2018/03/11/231241.jpg\" alt=\"Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Tu\u1ea5n anh, HAGL, D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh\" title=\"HLV Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi t\u00ean Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 Tu\u1ea5n Anh\">\r\n<em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i lu\u00f4n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o. HAGL c\u0169ng v\u1eady. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, <strong>t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 Tu\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t</strong>. Tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. C\u00f2n Tu\u1ea5n Anh d\u00f9 m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i tr\u00f2n vai.</em>\r\n<em>H\u00f4m nay ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Rimario v\u00ec th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u0169ng l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i</em><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, HAGL s\u1ebd h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n L\u1ea1ch Tray c\u1ee7a H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng FC. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, v\u00ec th\u1ebf th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch.</p>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-4-3-barca-danh-ao-so-7-cho-griezmann-c409a942583.html","id":"411"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y, ng\u00e0y 10/03/2018 06:01 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 10/3: HLV Pep Guardiola b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-944011\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-944011\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Pep Guardiola b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng.</strong> HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Man City v\u1eeba b\u1ecb L\u0110B\u0110 Anh \u201cs\u1edd g\u00e1y\u201d v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha m\u1eb7c \u00e1o c\u00f3 ruy-b\u0103ng m\u00e0u v\u00e0ng, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Catalunya. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, HLV Guardiola b\u1ecb gi\u1edbi quan ch\u1ee9c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh ph\u1ea1t 20.000 b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p t\u00e1i di\u1ec5n h\u00e0nh vi t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 10/3: HLV Pep Guardiola b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-10/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-10-3-HLV-Pep-Guardiola-bi-phat-nang-49fb570100000578-5482929-image-a-12_1520612365242-1520634559-438-width660height458.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">HLV Pep Guardiola b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Conte ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Kante, \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u0111\u1eebng m\u01a1.</strong> Theo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ee7a HLV Antonio Conte, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 N\u2019Golo Kante s\u1eafp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong th\u1eddi gian qua v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n, kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u0169ng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u0111\u1eebng m\u01a1 chuy\u1ec7n Chelsea b\u00e1n C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016/17.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Marco Reus kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn Real.</strong> Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00e0i hoa Marco Reus v\u1eeba k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Dortmund \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2023. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Reus chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 29, \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Dortmund t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2012.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Wilshere t\u00ednh r\u1eddi Arsenal mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed. </strong>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, Jack Wilshere chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Arsenal trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh n\u00e0y v\u1edbi \u201cPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7\u201d s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y k\u1ebft th\u00fac. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi AC Milan \u1edf c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Wilshere th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn anh \u0111ang t\u00ednh chuy\u1ec7n gia \u0111i. Jack Wilshere l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c di\u1ec7n c\u00e2y nh\u00e0 l\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1eddn, xu\u1ea5t th\u00e2n t\u1eeb l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Arsenal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Man City nh\u1eafm sao Brazil thay Yaya Toure. </strong>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Yaya Toure s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 35 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng sau v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c di\u1ec7n thanh l\u00fd. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 HLV Pep Guardiola mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Toure l\u00e0 sao tuy\u1ec3n Brazil hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang ch\u01a1i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Shakhtar, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Fred. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 24, hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn kh\u00e1c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"MU - Liverpool: \u201dXe bus\u201d Mourinho chi\u1ebfn \u201dch\u1ea5t rock\u201d Klopp\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-10/640c480-1520618879-183-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">MU - Liverpool: \u201dXe bus\u201d Mourinho chi\u1ebfn \u201dch\u1ea5t rock\u201d Klopp</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>(19h30, 10/3) Tr\u1eadn derby th\u1ee9 170 gi\u1eefa MU v\u00e0 Liverpool trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Anh.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-10-3-hlv-pep-guardiola-bi-phat-nang-c409a944011.html","id":"410"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u, ng\u00e0y 09/03/2018 05:04 AM (GMT+7)","title":"C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"https://cdn3.iconfinder.com/data/icons/tango-icon-library/48/software-update-available-256.png","new_desc":"<h3>Ra m\u1eaft phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n m\u1edbi</h3>\r\nAnh em t\u1ea3i app m\u1edbi v\u1ec1 t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y nha:\r\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.xembongda.xemworldcup&hl=vi\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.xembongda.xemworldcup&hl=vi</a>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-4-3-barca-danh-ao-so-7-cho-griezmann-c409a942583.html","id":"409"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u, ng\u00e0y 09/03/2018 05:04 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 9/3: Mahrez h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2i v\u1ec1 Man City","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-943758\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-943758\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Mahrez h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2i v\u1ec1 Man City.</strong> Riyad Mahrez \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi Leicester \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 Man City kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u00e1ng 1 v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 h\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng. \u201c\u0110\u1ebfn Man City s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ti\u1ebfc khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng thi\u1ebfu ch\u1eebng m\u1ef1c. May m\u1eafn khi CLB v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n t\u00f4i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch n\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t\u201d, Mahrez n\u00f3i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 9/3: Mahrez h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2i v\u1ec1 Man City - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\"  src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-08/3-8-2018-11-37-03-pm-660-1520527822-557-width660height495.jpg\" style=\"width: 660px; height: 495px;\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Riyad Mahrez</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Barca h\u1ebft mu\u1ed1n Bellerin</strong>. Theo t\u1edd Mundo Deportivo \u1edf Barcelona, Hector Bellerin \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Barcelona n\u1eefa do CLB quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd cho Nelson Semedo th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n. Semedo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mua trong h\u00e8 2017 nh\u01b0ng HLV Ernesto Valverde v\u1eabn ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu d\u00f9ng Sergi Roberto \u0111\u00e1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0 Semedo ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p xoay v\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kovacic \u201c\u0111\u1eaft h\u00e0ng\u201d \u1edf Serie A.</strong> Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 CLB c\u0169 Inter Milan, k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 AC Milan l\u1eabn AS Roma ch\u00e0o m\u1eddi quay l\u1ea1i Italia thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Kovacic ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng n\u1eafm v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Real Madrid v\u00e0 v\u1edbi tu\u1ed5i 24 s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 5 t\u1edbi, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u0111ang ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t CLB kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Reus quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng l\u1ee1 World Cup.</strong> Marco Reus cho bi\u1ebft anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t cho n\u0103m nay l\u00e0 gi\u1eef g\u00ecn th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c. Reus \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf World Cup 2014 l\u1eabn Euro 2016, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y anh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i k\u00e9o d\u00e0i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ghi 3 b\u00e0n trong 3 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Bundesliga cho Dortmund. \u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i World Cup, v\u00e0 m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng s\u1ebd tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ea3m m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ea3n tr\u1edf\u201d, Reus kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PSG v\u00e0 Basel b\u1ecb UEFA \u0111i\u1ec1u tra.</strong> UEFA \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf cu\u1ed9c \u0111i\u1ec1u tra v\u00e0o h\u00e0nh vi qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V hai \u0111\u1ed9i PSG v\u00e0 Basel \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c nh\u00f3m C\u0110V c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i v\u00e0 ri\u00eang PSG c\u00f2n b\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec1u tra \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 C\u0110V chi\u1ebfu laser v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Real Madrid.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 8/3: \u201dCh\u01a1i cho Mourinho th\u00edch h\u01a1n Klopp\u201d\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-08/1520510948-152-thumbnail.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 8/3: \u201dCh\u01a1i cho Mourinho th\u00edch h\u01a1n Klopp\u201d</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>C\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Man City, Danny Mills th\u00edch th\u00fa c\u00e1 t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Mourinho h\u01a1n Klopp.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-9-3-mahrez-hoi-han-doi-ve-man-city-c409a943758.html","id":"408"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 N\u0103m, ng\u00e0y 08/03/2018 05:04 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 8/3: B\u1ecb Real h\u1ea1 nh\u1ee5c, sao PSG th\u00e1o ch\u1ea1y","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-943513\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-943513\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>PSG b\u1ecb Real \u201ch\u1ea5t c\u1eb3ng\u201d, Di Maria t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tho\u00e1t th\u00e2n v\u1ec1&nbsp;Inter.&nbsp;</strong>Sau khi c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed tr\u1ea3i qua th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Angel Di Maria l\u1ea1i \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 8/3: B\u1ecb Real h\u1ea1 nh\u1ee5c, sao PSG th\u00e1o ch\u1ea1y - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-08/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-8-3-Bi-Real-ha-nhuc-sao-PSG-tim-duong-thao-chay-carvajal_jvjg-1520442733-727-width660height410.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Di Maria kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 khi c\u00f9ng PSG ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Real Madrid</p>\r\n\r\n<p>G\u0110TT Piero Ausilio cho bi\u1ebft Inter Milan s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Di Maria n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. Hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean Angel (ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 \u201cthi\u00ean th\u1ea7n\u201d) n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf PSG v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Arsenal nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi AC Milan:</strong> Theo tin t\u1eeb t\u1edd Goal, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i Hector Bellerin (Arsenal) s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi AC Milan t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00f2ng 1/8 Europa League v\u00e0o r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u t\u1edbi (9/3) v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n khoeo. Hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 HLV Arsene Wenger s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1 thay v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>David Luiz r\u1eddi Chelsea sang Barca:</strong> Trung v\u1ec7 David Luiz c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Barcelona \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 m\u1ed9t&nbsp;chuy\u00ean gia v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil hi v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc VCK World Cup 2018. Hi\u1ec7n Luiz kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Antonio Conte s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Chelsea v\u00ec m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u201cgi\u00e0\u201d nh\u1ea5t T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1\u2026 1 euro:</strong> Recreativo de Huelva \u2013 CLB v\u1eeba k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m 128 n\u0103m ng\u00e0y th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 12 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e2u \u0111\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha. H\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Huelva v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee9ng ra thanh to\u00e1n kho\u1ea3n n\u1ee3 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 7,6 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 mua l\u1ea1i CLB n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0ng l\u00e0\u2026 1 euro.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><div style=\"text-align: center;width: 100%;clear: both;position: relative;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"position:relative;max-width: 660px;margin: 0 auto\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 8/3: B\u1ecb Real h\u1ea1 nh\u1ee5c, sao PSG th\u00e1o ch\u1ea1y - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-08/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-8-3-Bi-Real-ha-nhuc-sao-PSG-tim-duong-thao-chay-49f93d8d00000578-5473463-huelva_city_council_have_-1520442733-722-width660height461.jpg\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image\" style=\"position: absolute;display: block;overflow: hidden;width: 660px;height: 90px;color: white;bottom: 0px;left: 0px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image-close\" style=\"top:5px;right: 5px;position: absolute;display: none;overflow: hidden;width: 22px;height: 22px;color: #ccc;font-size: large;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 8/3: B\u1ecb Real h\u1ea1 nh\u1ee5c, sao PSG th\u00e1o ch\u1ea1y - 3\" onclick=\"in_image_close();\" id=\"in-image-close\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/24h_banner_image_library/in-image-close.svg\"></img>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n                \r\n            </div></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-style: italic;\">S\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Estadio Nuevo Colombino c\u1ee7a Recreativo de Huelva - \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 1 euro c\u00f3 SV\u0110 s\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9a&nbsp;21.600 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd h\u1ee7y mua sao tr\u1ebb 30 tri\u1ec7u euro: </strong>Theo t\u1edd Marca, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro khi Barcelona h\u1ecfi mua Arthur Melo t\u1eeb Gremio v\u1edbi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng Gi\u00eang n\u0103m 2019 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Brazil \u0111\u00e3 bay sang T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n nh\u01b0ng hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i chung v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e0nh cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 21 tu\u1ed5i x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Samba.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Tottenham - Juventus: Pochettino e d\u00e8 Higuain\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-07/untitled-2-1520420160-51-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Tottenham - Juventus: Pochettino e d\u00e8 Higuain</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>(2h45, 8/3) HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Tottenham t\u1ecf ra lo ng\u1ea1i Higuain nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Juventus.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-8-3-bi-real-ha-nhuc-sao-psg-tim-duong-thao-chay-c409a943513.html","id":"407"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 T\u01b0, ng\u00e0y 07/03/2018 02:09 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 7/3: Hazard van n\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eddi Chelsea ngay v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-943275\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-943275\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Hazard kh\u1ea9n c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i tho\u00e1t ngay kh\u1ecfi Chelsea:</strong> Theo Jamie Carragher - c\u1ef1u trung v\u1ec7 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111ang l\u00e0 b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a k\u00eanh Sky Sports, ngay sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City, <strong>Eden Hazard </strong>\u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eddi \u201cThe Blues\u201d ngay:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y <em>(</em>Hazard)&nbsp;l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi b\u00e0n t\u00e1n v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c k\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, ngay khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1eddi b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb (sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Conte thay ra) ho\u1eb7c tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi lu\u00f4n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 n\u00f3i: \u201cH\u00e3y \u0111\u01b0a t\u00f4i \u0111i kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u00e2y ngay!\u201d</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 7/3: Hazard van n\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eddi Chelsea ngay v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-07/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-7-3-Hazard-van-nai-duoc-roi-Chelsea-ngay-va-luon-eden-hazard-1520360409-365-width660height402.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Hazard ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 b\u1ecb HLV Conte r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn Chelsea thua Man City</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>C\u1ef1u sao Serie A \u0111\u1ed9t t\u1eed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c an t\u00e1ng, ch\u1edd 2 th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa m\u1edbi bi\u1ebft nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n t\u1eed vong: </strong>T\u1edd Football-Italia cho hay, cu\u1ed9c kh\u00e1m nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eed thi c\u1ee7a Davide Astori \u2013 trung v\u1ec7 31 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Fiorentina v\u1eeba t\u1eed vong sau khi b\u1ecb ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n trong gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 \u1edf kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n Udine \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n trong h\u00f4m qua (6/3). Thi th\u1ec3 anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao tr\u1ea3 cho gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u00e0 l\u1ec5 tang s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 N\u0103m (8/3) \u1edf Florence.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean, theo Tr\u01b0\u1edfng C\u00f4ng t\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Udine - Antonio De Nicolo n\u00f3i v\u1edbi h\u00e3ng tin Ansa th\u00ec sau 60 ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 c\u00e1i ch\u1ebft c\u1ee7a Astori m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5. Hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 anh b\u1ecb tr\u1ee5y tim \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n hay c\u00f3 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i (c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ee5 \u00e1n m\u1ea1ng) g\u00e2y t\u1eed vong.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>S\u1eafp \u0111\u1ebfn Barca, sao tr\u1ebb 30 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u1eabn lo ngay ng\u00e1y:</strong> Theo Arthur Melo \u2013 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 21 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Gremio th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n CLB Brazil \u0111\u00e3 bay \u0111\u1ebfn Barcelona \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Th\u1ec3 thao Barca Robert Fernandez v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Mundo Deportivo cho hay, Arthur s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Nou Camp v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n anh v\u1eabn \u0111ang r\u1ea5t lo l\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>C\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c fan l\u00e0m lo\u1ea1n khi Man City \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u MU: </strong>C\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t Manchester \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch an ninh l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an to\u00e0n cho tr\u1eadn derby th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 n\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 5h30 ng\u00e0y 7/4 theo gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Man City s\u1ebd gi\u01a1 cao chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3. N\u00f3 s\u1ebd t\u0103ng th\u00eam s\u1ef1 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 th\u00f9 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1eefa fan 2 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a CLB n\u00e0y v\u00e0 C\u0110V c\u1ee7a MU - \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Pep xem Man City v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a hay b\u1eb1ng Barca:</strong> Man xanh c\u1ee7a HLV Pep Guardiola v\u1eabn \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao \u1edf c\u1ea3 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh l\u1eabn Champions League. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean cho ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, Pep cho r\u1eb1ng Man City c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Barca.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Chelsea r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n: D\u00e0n sao h\u00f2 nhau l\u1eadt gh\u1ebf Conte, Barca \u0111\u00e2m lo s\u1ee3\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-06/1520301962-220-thumbnail.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Chelsea r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n: D\u00e0n sao h\u00f2 nhau l\u1eadt gh\u1ebf Conte, Barca \u0111\u00e2m lo s\u1ee3</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Conte c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Chelsea t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u Barca \u1edf Champions League.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-7-3-hazard-van-nai-duoc-roi-chelsea-ngay-va-luon-c409a943275.html","id":"406"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 Ba, ng\u00e0y 06/03/2018 02:50 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 6/3: SAO PSG \u0111e d\u1ecda Real Madrid","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-943035\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-943035\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>SAO PSG \u0111e d\u1ecda Real Madrid:</strong> PSG \u0111\u00e3 thua 1-3 trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Dani Alves kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 v\u1eady. Trong b\u00e0i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil cho r\u1eb1ng PSG s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng minh cho Real v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u th\u1ea5y PSG kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 6/3: SAO PSG \u0111e d\u1ecda Real Madrid - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-06/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-6-3-SAO-PSG-de-doa-Real-Madrid-hot-dani-1520279281-370-width660height475.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Dani Alves t\u1ef1 tin ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng Real Madrid</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Guardiola b\u1ecb FA \"tu\u00fdt c\u00f2i\":</strong> Trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Chelsea \u0111\u00eam Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt, HLV Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i v\u1edbi d\u1ea3i ruy b\u0103ng m\u00e0u v\u00e0ng tr\u00ean ng\u1ef1c \u00e1o. Th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Pep nh\u1eb1m \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 phong tr\u00e0o Catalunya ly khai nh\u01b0ng Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch hi\u1ec7p h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh, \u00f4ng Martin Glenn cho r\u1eb1ng bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi huy hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c kh\u1ee7ng b\u1ed1 ISIS.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Liverpool kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea5u MU: </strong>Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng Porto 5-0 v\u00e0 coi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng HLV Klopp s\u1ebd c\u1ea5t gi\u1eef nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00e0nh s\u1ee9c cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p MU cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n. Tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng Porto v\u00e0 tung ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i s\u00f2ng ph\u1eb3ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Man City \u0111\u00f3n vi\u1ec7n binh 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng:</strong> M\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, Man City \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Mendy t\u1eeb Monaco. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng. Sau th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb, Mendy \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n sau.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Balotelli s\u1eafp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Serie A:</strong> Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi 14 l\u1ea7n l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng, chi\u1ebfm 41% t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Nice t\u1ea1i Ligue 1 m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap \"Ng\u1ef1a ch\u1ee9ng\" l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 Juventus v\u00e0 Napoli. Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Italia cho hay, kh\u00f4ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Balotelli s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Serie A m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Nh\u1eafm \u201cHarry Kane\u201d n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c, xong tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup 2018\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-06/leipzigs-striker-timo-werner-celebrates640x480-1520269448-237-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Nh\u1eafm \u201cHarry Kane\u201d n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c, xong tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup 2018</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Timo Werner \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 Harry Kane n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 \u0111ang th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-6-3-sao-psg-de-doa-real-madrid-c409a943035.html","id":"405"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 Hai, ng\u00e0y 05/03/2018 05:05 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 5/3: Anh trai Messi b\u1ecb b\u1eaft v\u00ec \u201cph\u00ea c\u1ea7n\u201d, \u0111\u00e2m xe","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-942782\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-942782\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Anh ru\u1ed9t Messi b\u1ecb b\u1eaft kh\u1ea9n c\u1ea5p v\u00ec d\u00f9ng ma t\u00fay, g\u00e2y tai n\u1ea1n: </strong>Trong khi Lionel Messi v\u1eeba ghi b\u00e0n quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap Barcelona th\u1eafng Atletico Madrid \u1edf v\u00f2ng 27 La Liga th\u00ec t\u1ea1i qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 Argentina, tin d\u1eef t\u1eeb gia \u0111\u00ecnh anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 5/3: Anh trai Messi b\u1ecb b\u1eaft v\u00ec \u201cph\u00ea c\u1ea7n\u201d, \u0111\u00e2m xe - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-05/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-5-3-Anh-trai-Messi-bi-bat-vi-phe-can-dam-xe-120171202085257-1520196545-882-width660height359.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh trai Matias l\u00e0m x\u1ea5u m\u1eb7t Lionel Messi v\u00e0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh si\u00eau sao n\u00e0y</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo 2 t\u1edd Ol\u00e9 v\u00e0 Telam, m\u1ed9t trong hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh ru\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Leo l\u00e0 Matias Messi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c l\u00e0 d\u00ednh l\u00edu tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00e2m xe \u00f4 t\u00f4 \u1edf Buenos Aires v\u00e0 b\u1ecb nh\u00e2n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb anh \u0111e d\u1ecda b\u1eb1ng s\u00fang. Matias b\u1ecb b\u1eaft ngay \u1edf hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n c\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng cho th\u1ea5y anh \u0111\u00e3 h\u00fat c\u1ea7n sa khi l\u00e1i xe \u00f4 t\u00f4 g\u00e2y \u00e1n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 5/3: Anh trai Messi b\u1ecb b\u1eaft v\u00ec \u201cph\u00ea c\u1ea7n\u201d, \u0111\u00e2m xe - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-05/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-5-3-Anh-trai-Messi-bi-bat-vi-phe-can-dam-xe-15201787212603-1520196545-208-width660height371.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Chi\u1ebfc xe g\u00e2y tai n\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a Matias Messi</p><p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>16 n\u0103m r\u1ed3i, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Arsenal m\u1edbi t\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady: </strong>Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ee7i h\u1ed5 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00e2n binh Brighton &amp; Hove Albion \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 11 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, \u201cPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7\u201d kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi, ngang b\u1eb1ng chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn b\u1ebft b\u00e1t nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 2 n\u0103m 2002 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ebfn nay.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c bu\u1ed3n v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ee9 4 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 10 n\u0103m 2002.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><div style=\"text-align: center;width: 100%;clear: both;position: relative;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"position:relative;max-width: 660px;margin: 0 auto\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 5/3: Anh trai Messi b\u1ecb b\u1eaft v\u00ec \u201cph\u00ea c\u1ea7n\u201d, \u0111\u00e2m xe - 3\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-05/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-5-3-Anh-trai-Messi-bi-bat-vi-phe-can-dam-xe-1520172509585_lc_galleryimage_brighton_hove_albion-1520196545-25-width660height421.jpg\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image\" style=\"position: absolute;display: block;overflow: hidden;width: 660px;height: 90px;color: white;bottom: 0px;left: 0px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image-close\" style=\"top:5px;right: 5px;position: absolute;display: none;overflow: hidden;width: 22px;height: 22px;color: #ccc;font-size: large;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 5/3: Anh trai Messi b\u1ecb b\u1eaft v\u00ec \u201cph\u00ea c\u1ea7n\u201d, \u0111\u00e2m xe - 4\" onclick=\"in_image_close();\" id=\"in-image-close\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/24h_banner_image_library/in-image-close.svg\"></img>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n                \r\n            </div></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Arsenal thua nh\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton &amp; Hove Albion</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mbappe d\u1ec5 n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t bu\u1ed3n Neymar, l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n \u0111\u1ea5u Real:</strong> Theo ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean Julien Maynard c\u1ee7a t\u1edd T\u00e9l\u00e9foot s\u1ed1ng g\u1ea7n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh Kylian Mbappe th\u00ec t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eaft c\u00e1 ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng PSG t\u1eed chi\u1ebfn Real Madrid \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Neymar \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 h\u1ebft m\u00f9a \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea1n x\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn PSG kh\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed1n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Griezman, Messi mu\u1ed1n sao kh\u00e1c t\u1eeb Atletico \u0111\u1ebfn Barca: </strong>Theo t\u1edd Don Balon, d\u00f9 Barca \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y cho Antoine Griezmann t\u1eeb Atletico Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro nh\u01b0ng Lionel Messi mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i m\u00ecnh mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Saul Niguez h\u01a1n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Iniesta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 sang Man City:</strong> T\u1edd The Mirror \u0111\u01b0a tin, HLV Pep Guardiola mu\u1ed1n h\u1ed9i ng\u1ed9 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf Barca l\u00e0 Andres Iniesta khi mu\u1ed1n m\u1eddi anh gia nh\u1eadp Man City h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Khi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 33 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd v\u1edbi Barca th\u00e1ng 10 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n r\u00e0ng bu\u1ed9c b\u1eaft anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Nou Camp \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"G\u00f3c chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt Barca \u2013 Atletico: Messi t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ed1ng t\u1eeb b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-05/1520193786-401-thumbnail.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">G\u00f3c chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt Barca \u2013 Atletico: Messi t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ed1ng t\u1eeb b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Atletico \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 cho Messi \"gi\u1edf b\u00e0i t\u1ee7\" \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t cho Barca.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-5-3-anh-trai-messi-bi-bat-vi-phe-can-dam-xe-c409a942782.html","id":"404"},{"date":"Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt, ng\u00e0y 04/03/2018 05:05 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 4/3: Barca d\u00e0nh \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 cho Griezmann","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-942583\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-942583\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Barca d\u00e0nh \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 cho Griezmann?</strong> T\u1edd AS cho bi\u1ebft n\u1ebfu (ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t khi) Antoine Griezmann r\u1eddi Atletico \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Barcelona, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 c\u1ee7a CLB. H\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1 Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ng\u0103n Philippe Coutinho l\u1ea5y \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00e0nh cho Griezmann.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 4/3: Barca d\u00e0nh \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 cho Griezmann - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\"  src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-03/skysports-antoine-griezmann-atletico-madrid-la-liga_4243441-660-1520095463-527-width660height495.jpg\" style=\"width: 660px; height: 495px;\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Antoine Griezmann</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Man City mua h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf</strong>. Pep Guardiola trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n ng\u1eafn cho t\u1edd Telegraph cho bi\u1ebft trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y Man City s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o 1-2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd mua \u00edt v\u00e0 mua r\u1ebb h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i\u201d, Pep n\u00f3i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Heynckes \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb Lewandowski t\u1ea1m qu\u00ean Real.</strong> Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n Robert Lewandowski s\u1ebd v\u1ec1 Real Madrid sau khi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u1ecfi Bayern Munich, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HLV Jupp Heynckes \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf quan \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan n\u00ean t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi g\u00e1c chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai sang m\u1ed9t b\u00ean. \u201cKhi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 cho Bayern th\u00ec anh ta ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung t\u1ed1i \u0111a cho Bayern\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Si\u00eau c\u00f2 xui Donnarumma r\u1eddi Milan.</strong> Trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n cho \u0111\u00e0i ph\u00e1t thanh Rai Sport \u1edf Italia, \u201csi\u00eau c\u00f2\u201d Mino Raiola b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Gianluigi Donnarumma d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn \u1edf l\u1ea1i AC Milan trong h\u00e8 2017 v\u1eabn n\u00ean r\u1eddi s\u00e2n San Siro \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. \u201cN\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00f3i mu\u1ed1n \u0111i t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c, s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb r\u1ea5t h\u1eadu h\u0129nh cho Gigio\u201d, Raiola n\u00f3i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>VAR s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng \u1edf World Cup 2018.</strong> Ban ch\u1ea5p h\u00e0nh Hi\u1ec7p h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf IFAB \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ed th\u00f4ng qua quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 video tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i VAR s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho World Cup 2018. VAR \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Bundesliga, Serie A, MSL, gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Australia v\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00fap \u1edf Anh, v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean IFAB. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch FIFA Gianni Infantino \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1: \u201cS\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i trong th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, nh\u01b0ng VAR \u0111\u01b0a ch\u00fang ta t\u1edbi g\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u0111\u00f3 h\u01a1n\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 3/3: Pep g\u1ecdi Conte l\u00e0 thi\u00ean t\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-03/1520079243-674-thumbnail.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 3/3: Pep g\u1ecdi Conte l\u00e0 thi\u00ean t\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>HLV Pep Guardiola n\u1ee9c n\u1edf khen Conte tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Man City - Chelsea.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-4-3-barca-danh-ao-so-7-cho-griezmann-c409a942583.html","id":"402"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y, ng\u00e0y 03/03/2018 05:49 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: C\u1ef1u sao \"Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\" b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khuy\u00ean Pogba \u0111\u1ebfn Man City","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-942434\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-942434\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>C\u1ef1u sao MU b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khuy\u00ean Pogba \u0111\u1ebfn Man City</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU, Paul Ince kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e0n em Paul Pogba h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Man City h\u01a1n MU. B\u1edfi l\u1ebd, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p&nbsp;c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i g\u00f2 m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: C\u1ef1u sao &amp;#34;Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&amp;#34; b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khuy\u00ean Pogba \u0111\u1ebfn Man City - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-03/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Cuu-sao-paul-pogba-manchester-united_fx843m3kfmjo1vt7n8lnr-1520083678-973-width660height371.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Pogba kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 nu\u00f4ng chi\u1ec1u \u1edf MU</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>B\u00e1o nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Ibra cho MU</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau khi HLV Jose Mourinho tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \"l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng\" Zlatan Ibrahimovic s\u1ebd r\u1eddi MU h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, t\u1edd Manchester Evening News - t\u1edd b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng&nbsp;chuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a tin li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn MU v\u00e0 Man City \u0111\u00e3 cho r\u1eb1ng \"Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\" ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua Antoine Griezmann (Atletico Madrid), Mauro Icardi (Inter Milan), Ciro Immobile (Lazio) ho\u1eb7c trao nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Marcus Rashford.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Liverpool ng\u0103n Kroos \u0111\u1ebfn Old Trafford</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo&nbsp;chuy\u00ean gia Steve Nicol - ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Liverpool th\u00ec Real Madrid c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ea1nh h\u00e8 n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng b\u00e1n Toni Kroos cho MU l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean. Trong khi \u1ea5y, BL\u0110 \"Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\" s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>De Gea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Guillem Balague, chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi&nbsp;T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eadt m\u00ed tin c\u1ef1c vui cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9&nbsp;MU&nbsp;v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a David De Gea. Theo \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e2y vi\u1ebft b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng tr\u00ean Sky Sports cho r\u1eb1ng De Gea s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi \"Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\" thay v\u00ec s\u1ebd sang Real Madrid h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\"V\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a De Gea v\u00e0 Hazard. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng&nbsp;De Gea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Man United. V\u1edbi Hazard, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t Galacticos m\u1edbi v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng ch\u1edd xem \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y,\"&nbsp;Balague cho hay tr\u00ean Sky Sports.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, De Gea t\u1eebng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.&nbsp;\"Th\u1eddi gian tr\u00f4i qua th\u1eadt nhanh. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 CLB \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7 n\u0103m v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea3y \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi t\u00f4i - t\u1ed1t c\u00f3 x\u1ea5u c\u00f3..., song t\u00f4i th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i \u1edf ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>T\u00f4i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 United tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u01a1n,\"&nbsp;th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 27 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi Daily Star.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, theo Goal,&nbsp; De Gea s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n giao k\u00e8o m\u1edbi n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 350.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, thay v\u00ec con s\u1ed1 275.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb \"Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.\"</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mourinho mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi thay De Gea</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \"D\u1ea3i ng\u00e2n h\u00e0 3.0\" v\u00e0 De Gea l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng mi\u1ebfng gh\u00e9p quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Real Madrid s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 MU 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: C\u1ef1u sao &amp;#34;Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&amp;#34; b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khuy\u00ean Pogba \u0111\u1ebfn Man City - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-03/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Mourinho-mua-thu-mon-dat-nhat-the-gioi-thay-De-Gea-660mu-stegen-1520048447-150-width660height441.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Ter Stegen \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p x\u1ea5u nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thay th\u1ebf th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. T\u1edd Goal ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, MU s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7 khi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb mua Ter Stegen c\u1ee7a Barca 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 bi\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tranh sao Napoli v\u1edbi Liverpool</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh. Liverpool \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0o nh\u1eb1m thay th\u1ebf Emre Can ch\u01b0a ch\u1ecbu gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean MU s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu khoanh tay \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u00ecn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HLV Mourinho c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Carrick s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 c\u00f2n Fellaini ra \u0111i. T\u1edd Daily Star cho hay, MU s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ph\u00e1 gi\u00e1 Liverpool khi \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Cu\u1ed7m si\u00eau trung v\u1ec7 Umtiti kh\u1ecfi Barca nh\u01b0 Neymar</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo t\u1edd The Sun, MU \u0111ang t\u00ednh chuy\u1ec7n k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti, trng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Old Trafford. Sau 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi HLV Mourinho. \u0110i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa Umtiti v\u1edbi Barca tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch PSG \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Neymar Junior m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2017, v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 222 tri\u1ec7u euro.</p><p></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><div style=\"text-align: center;width: 100%;clear: both;position: relative;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"position:relative;max-width: 660px;margin: 0 auto\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: C\u1ef1u sao &amp;#34;Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&amp;#34; b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khuy\u00ean Pogba \u0111\u1ebfn Man City - 3\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-03/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Hoc-PSG-Neymar-cuom-sieu-trung-ve-cua-Barca-nintchdbpict000375417186-1520017284-65-width660height440.jpg\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image\" style=\"position: absolute;display: block;overflow: hidden;width: 660px;height: 90px;color: white;bottom: 0px;left: 0px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image-close\" style=\"top:5px;right: 5px;position: absolute;display: none;overflow: hidden;width: 22px;height: 22px;color: #ccc;font-size: large;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: C\u1ef1u sao &amp;#34;Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&amp;#34; b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khuy\u00ean Pogba \u0111\u1ebfn Man City - 4\" onclick=\"in_image_close();\" id=\"in-image-close\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/24h_banner_image_library/in-image-close.svg\"></img>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n                \r\n            </div></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Umtiti l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a HLV Mourinho</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Shakhtar c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc b\u00e1n SAO Brazil cho MU</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, Fred \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Carrick v\u00e0 Fellaini. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 MU m\u00e0 ngay c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 l\u00e0 Man City c\u0169ng \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 25 n\u00e0y. T\u1edd Manchester Evening News cho hay, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ukraine \u01b0u ti\u00ean b\u00e1n Fred cho MU do \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Marcos Rojo h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf MU</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, trung v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u do di ch\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Rojo, t\u00ednh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Sporting Lisbon n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Argentina kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Old Trafford v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ra \u0111i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mourinho th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c v\u1edbi Fellaini</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>HLV Jose Mourinho v\u1eeba th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn, MU s\u1eafp m\u1ea5t Marouane Fellaini ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8. Sau 5 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 t\u00ednh chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i do kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi BL\u0110 MU. Trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng, c\u00f3 tin Arsenal t\u1eebng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Fellaini nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh. V\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 7 t\u1edbi, \u201c\u0110\u1ea7u x\u00f9\u201d \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef1 do k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Darmian \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1ec1 Juventus</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo Football Italia, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Matteo Darmian \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n m\u00e0 ph\u00eda Juventus \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi MU, Darmian thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Torino, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a th\u00e0nh Turin. D\u00f9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia kh\u00e1c, Darmian v\u1eabn \u01b0u ti\u00ean tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Bom t\u1ea5n Robben \u0111\u1ebfn MU: Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, kh\u1ecfi c\u1ea7n Gareth Bale\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-02/news_176770_1-640x480-1519932223-593-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Bom t\u1ea5n Robben \u0111\u1ebfn MU: Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, kh\u1ecfi c\u1ea7n Gareth Bale</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>K\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arjen Robben, MU s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 mua th\u00eam Gareth Bale.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"chuyen-nhuong-mu-hoc-psg-neymar-cuom-sieu-trung-ve-cua-barca-c409a942434.html","id":"401"}]}